Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:04.03,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa, can I have your autograph while I have the chance? {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:06.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What doting parents. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:09.58,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Same thing will happen to you once you have a daughter, too. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I swear it won't. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:13.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I can see you having one, {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,since you are very much like Dad. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:17.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What? Me and him?! {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:19.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Two months, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:21.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, it's been two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.43,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You will have the baby, right? {ep14}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:25.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.64,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's a piece of work, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:28.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun will be there for me, so I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:37.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We worked together until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.65,San,San,0,0,0,,He looks just like you on that day, Akio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:47.82,San,San,0,0,0,,When I had Nagisa in my stomach, you said that you'd protect her. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:49.16,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I did, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:54.32,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Good luck, you bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:56.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"Bum..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:59.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I'm not allowed to be one anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:02.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa will probably have to take a break from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:06.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll have to support three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is where the trial for my family begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:12.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A thought crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:17.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did my old man think the same thing before I was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.65,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.15,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I heard you had a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:56.94,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.86,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Your wife had a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.66,Default,John,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Mr. Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's not born yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san, who did you hear it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.83,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,My wife heard it from Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.75,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Everyone in the neighborhood knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To be feared: the power of neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:19.34,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You've still got a way to go as a member of society,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.01,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,but now you'll have to act like\Na real husband no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah... but it doesn't feel real to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:30.02,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You'll feel that no matter what once the baby's born.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:34.02,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,No one in this world can live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:39.03,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Everyone lives by supporting\Nand being supported by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.49,Default-alt,Guy,0,0,0,,There he goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:43.49,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It's been 4.5 billion years since the Earth was formed in this vast universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:46.16,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 15
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:46.16,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}As a Summer Memory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The days started to move at an amazing speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:55.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,{\fs81}By the time she entered the third month, the pregnancy sickness worsened and Nagisa spent most days in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:59.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry; I can take care of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're supposed to do this together, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you eat at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I couldn't eat much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Isn't there any way to make this a little easier for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:21.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's not even known why pregnancy sickness happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:26.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Drinking water only makes me sick, so I take these to get water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:36.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. Did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm feeling all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You should eat some, even a little, while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Did you make these?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:11.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not used to it, so the shape is a little... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:14.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,While the days went flying by,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa and I were restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is it all right for you to be up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I feel very good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:42.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The doctor said that things will stabilize around the tenth week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,He was exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:47.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Must mean it's growing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, I have something I wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Give birth at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:01.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. I want to give birth to the baby here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can you even do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:07.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I got this pamphlet for a maternity class yesterday at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:12.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,There's a page by a mother who gave birth at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:18.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So the father gives the first bath, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:23.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,At a hospital, there are cases where you can't hold the baby immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I would like to be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This is your and my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:41.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to give birth to the baby in our home. In this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.47,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Give birth at home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.14,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,How was that drift?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How about you turn off the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:04.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You know, giving birth is hard enough,\N{\i1}and{\i0\fscx30} {\r} you're gonna try to pull it off at your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:08.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The doctor is worried about Nagisa's health,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,but I want to fulfill Nagisa's wishes as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That said, of course it's a question of how well she is at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:20.54,San,San,0,0,0,,You're right. Having a safe delivery is the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:26.42,San,San,0,0,0,,But when I gave birth to Nagisa, I was soon separated from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:31.89,San,San,0,0,0,,Akio-san held Nagisa after the doctors, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:34.64,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But I was the first one to lick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You licked me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:39.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You were that cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You can't do such a thing even if I was cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.40,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you agree to giving birth at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.41,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If there's nothing to worry about, physically, then why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.49,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Make sure you give the first hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.41,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:58.54,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'll be the first to lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No. Tomoya-kun also gets the first lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I won't be licking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Ah, right. He won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What a stupid family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.14,San,San,0,0,0,,This is Yagi-san. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:18.18,San,San,0,0,0,,She is my friend and works as a midwife. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.52,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,I'm Yagi. Nice to meet you. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm Okazaki Nagisa. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm her husband, Tomoya. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:29.65,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,I was told you were looking into delivering the baby here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:33.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can it be done in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:35.95,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,What's important is to be in a place where you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.08,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.29,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Please take the time to think things through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.42,Default,2,0,0,0,,We'll be in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.05,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,If anything happens, please let me know any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.59,San,San,0,0,0,,Yagi-san knows that Nagisa has a weak body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:09:01.18,San,San,0,0,0,,{\fs75.6}If those around worry about it too much, the mother becomes uneasy, too, so I was told to be mindful of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:11.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What were you talking about with Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Um... Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:18.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You don't need to hide it; it was about my health, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:24.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I know how you, Mom, and Dad are all worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:28.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, even if the worst happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to give birth to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're all working so you have a safe delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:43.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Doesn't this remind you of our high school days?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:48.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:53.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Remember how we all worked together to make the stage a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I just thought that it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.04,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Can you tell? I'm your daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You can't tell lies like that; the baby will believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.92,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Your kid can't even take a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's Nagisa's baby, so it probably can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:20.43,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.77,San,San,0,0,0,,Apparently Akio-san wants to be called "Akki".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:26.35,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Akki. I'm Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Quit the prenatal training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:33.65,San,San,0,0,0,,The ears are there by this time,\Nand it can hear the sounds from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.57,San,San,0,0,0,,so it's good to let it listen to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:39.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm always singing songs to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:46.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Dango, dango, dango, dango,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:50.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Big Dango Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:57.26,Default,All,0,0,0,,Dango, dango, dango, dango,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:01.30,Default,All,0,0,0,,Big Dango Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:08.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I thought everything was going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Or, perhaps somewhere in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was eagerly anticipating that day coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I just got a little sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.20,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa called in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:28.33,San,San,0,0,0,,I rushed over, and Nagisa was on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then you could have told me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:34.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry; I didn't want to disturb you at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.30,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Please don't worry; the baby's well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.89,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Call me at any time anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:49.39,San,San,0,0,0,,To be on the safe side, I'll be with Nagisa during the day from tomorrow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.31,San,San,0,0,0,,That way you'll rest easy, right, Tomoya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:00.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How are you feeling? Is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:06.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't need anything.\NI'm at ease when you're by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:10.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of course. Since you're strong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please don't worry, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:27.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can make it through if we're together, since I'm being protected by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:38.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was no longer able to relax in the blessed feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.83,San,San,0,0,0,,Tomoya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.21,San,San,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.84,San,San,0,0,0,,So this is where Nagisa was working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.67,San,San,0,0,0,,I wanted to come here once, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.38,San,San,0,0,0,,It's a very trendy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No one uses that word nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.01,San,San,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.23,San,San,0,0,0,,I have something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:16.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.73,San,San,0,0,0,,It's about Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:26.49,San,San,0,0,0,,I was told by the doctor that there will be some danger during the delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.74,San,San,0,0,0,,I have not told this to Nagisa yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.29,San,San,0,0,0,,Only I've been told.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:39.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Exactly how much danger is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't say even Nagisa's life is at...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:48.68,San,San,0,0,0,,The stress to the mother will be greater than an average delivery's,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:52.14,San,San,0,0,0,,but there shouldn't be any problem with the delivery itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.48,San,San,0,0,0,,However that's if everything goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:02.15,San,San,0,0,0,,As you know, Nagisa falls ill from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:06.78,San,San,0,0,0,,There are many mysterious aspects to Nagisa's illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.87,San,San,0,0,0,,and the doctors are worried about the worst-case scenario, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:17.25,San,San,0,0,0,,This is something that needs to be thought through carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:21.50,San,San,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to tell you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:28.01,San,San,0,0,0,,You should tell Nagisa, and both of you should go listen to what the doctor has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.51,San,San,0,0,0,,After that, let's all think together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If we think of the worst-case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,should we give up on having the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.11,San,San,0,0,0,,I cannot answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.82,San,San,0,0,0,,But, if that's the choice to make, then the sooner the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.41,San,San,0,0,0,,Please think it through carefully with Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:56.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san, as always, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.04,San,San,0,0,0,,We're a family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to have the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I knew you would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:13.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I am a weak person, but I don't want to give up on the baby because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:18.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If it's to have the baby, then I don't mind giving up on delivering here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:19.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to meet the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What did the doctor say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:33.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They said the risk would go down if she delivered at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I'm still worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.46,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nagisa didn't change her mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think in her heart, she's scared, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's acting cheerful, but I think she may be feeling the same things as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.44,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Come with me for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.61,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.87,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This is my secret playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:21.87,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I play baseball with kids or sit and do nothing here a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:26.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I noticed you went missing during work a lot, so this is where you were, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.72,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The trees and bushes got torn down one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:32.72,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,...and apparently a hospital's going to be built here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:29.72,Default-alt,Kids,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.84,Default-alt,Kids,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.84,Default-alt,Kid,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.35,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's a great thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.22,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.85,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This is the continuation of something I told you two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:47.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's when I was still in theater and Sanae was a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:53.32,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,As I told you, Nagisa was always alone back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:59.95,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That day, Sanae and I left for work, leaving the sick Nagisa at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.92,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We both couldn't skip work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:09.88,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nagisa's condition looked stable, and both Sanae and I were planning to come home right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.76,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nagisa was outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.76,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,She was waiting until she collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.27,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,By the time morning came,\Nit looked like there was no hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.77,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I never went through anything that sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:29.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This will be the first time I've told the story from this point on to anyone but Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:35.03,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, I was running with Nagisa in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:40.41,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I was running aimlessly, and I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:42.91,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I prayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.29,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"Please save Nagisa."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.46,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,"I don't want an ending like this."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:52.51,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,All I could do was pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:18:01.18,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Right then, it felt like the plants here covered Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.27,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I thought I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:13.94,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But it was reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:18.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Tears overwhelmed me,\Nand I thanked everything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.95,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I've been looking after this place ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:27.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but to think of this place as Nagisa's double.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.25,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Strange story, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But it really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:39.93,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's impossible for all wishes to come true if you pray for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:47.19,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But if you think and put your best effort forth until the end, then the outcome can't be that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:51.27,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you to have the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'm saying leave the judgment to the one who goes through the most pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:57.20,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,and we'll just accept the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.74,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Or rather, Tomoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:05.41,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'm sure there will be lots of hardships and painful stuff waiting for you ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You guys can...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:10.79,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We can overcome them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We're a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.09,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We're going to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:32.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The wind feels nice and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It just moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:42.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:45.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It felt like I was rubbed from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:47.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,How about we come up with a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:03.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll need one if it's a boy and another if it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:07.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,How about we use one character from your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:12.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, rather than that, let's think of\Nsomething from your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can pass on the last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:19.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But it's difficult to use my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It'd become like Nagisako or Nagisami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't have to use it literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Something that traces back to Nagisa should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,How does Ushio sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:43.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. It's about how the tide rises and goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:50.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If it's this, it can be used for a boy or a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okazaki Ushio, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sure a lot will happen within a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:05.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But as time passes, things will return to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:10.12,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That will continue, and I will watch over Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:14.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Rather than a "nagisa", a bay, "ushio" is more grand, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since it's the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:25.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will it be able to grow up to be someone with the kindness to embrace and nurture anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I hope it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:32.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We couldn't go to the beach again this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:33.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:37.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I wanted to see the ocean with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then let's make a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:40.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:44.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Next year, we'll go to the beach with Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,A promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You will promise to, won't you, Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:59.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I promise.
