Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:49.94,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,There's a theory of multiple worlds existing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:51.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fujibayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:55.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I remember you saying something like that when you were talking about fortune-telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:24:00.74,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes. There is no one future,\Nbut there are many possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:02.37,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I still think that.
